In [ ]:
def synthetic_target_edge_image(shape: tuple[int, int], target_geometry: BaseGeometry,
                                target_genome: BaseGenome) -> np.array:
    edge_image = np.zeros(shape, dtype=np.uint8)
    A, t, r, d = CameraTranslator().translate_genome(target_genome)
    render_geometry_with_camera(edge_image, target_geometry, A, t, r, d, (255,))
    return edge_image
In [ ]:
def synthetic_target_dna(shape: tuple[int, int]):
    fu = max(shape) - 100
    fv = fu
    h, w = shape
    cx, cy = w // 2, h // 2
    tx, ty, tz = 0.00, 2.35, 8.40
    rx, ry, rz = 0.29, 0.00, 0.00
    d0, d1, d2, d3, d4 = np.zeros(5)
    camera_dna = np.array([fu, fv, cx, cy, tx, ty, tz, rx, ry, rz, d0, d1, d2, d3, d4])
    return camera_dna
In [ ]:
def add_noise_to_image(original_image: np.array, noise_image: np.array) -> np.array:
    noisy_edge_image = original_image + noise_image
    noisy_edge_image = cv.threshold(noisy_edge_image, 0, 255, cv.THRESH_BINARY)[1].astype(np.uint8)
    return noisy_edge_image

image_shape = (image_height, image_width) = 600, 800
geometry_file = f"{DATA_FOLDER}/squash/geometries/full_squash_court.obj"
parameters_file = f"{DATA_FOLDER}/squash/squash_parameters.json"
In [ ]:
fitting_geometry = ObjGeometry(geometry_file)
real_geometry = fitting_geometry  # Ideally, the target geometry is the fitting geometry
real_dna = synthetic_target_dna(image_shape)

genome_parameters = CameraGenomeParameters(parameters_file, image_shape)
camera_genome_factory = CameraGenomeFactory(genome_parameters)

real_genome = camera_genome_factory.create(real_dna, "target_camera")

edge_image = synthetic_target_edge_image(image_shape, real_geometry, real_genome)

noise_dict = {
    "No Noise": NoNoise(),
    "Salt": SaltNoise(0.01),
    "Horizontal": HLinesNoise(spacing=128),
    "Vertical": VLinesNoise(spacing=128),
    "Grid": GridNoise(hspacing=128, vspacing=128, angle=0),
    "Rotated Grid": GridNoise(hspacing=128, vspacing=128, angle=45)
}

distance_type = DistanceMap.DistanceType.L2
log_div = 0.3
strategy = DistanceMapWithPunishment(distance_type, log_div)

fig, ax = plt.subplots(2, 3, sharex=True, sharey=True)
for i, (k, n) in enumerate(noise_dict.items()):
    noise_image = n.generate_noise(edge_image)
    final_image = add_noise_to_image(edge_image, noise_image)

    F = strategy.create_fitness(final_image)

    r = i // 3
    c = i % 3
    ax[r][c].imshow(F, cmap="RdYlBu", vmin=-1, vmax=1)
    ax[r][c].set_title(k)
    ax[r][c].set_axis_off()
scl = 1
fig.set_size_inches(3.50*scl,2.695*scl)
fig.tight_layout()
fig.subplots_adjust(wspace=0.05, hspace=-0.3)

save_figure(fig, f"{OUTPUT_FOLDER}/noises.eps")
